# Vercel Web Analytics Implementation Report

## Summary
Verified and confirmed that Vercel Web Analytics is already properly installed and configured in this Next.js project.

## Current Status
The project already has Vercel Web Analytics fully configured according to the latest official documentation from https://vercel.com/docs/analytics/quickstart

## What Was Found
1. **Package Already Installed**: `@vercel/analytics` v2.0.1 is present in package.json
2. **Analytics Component Already Implemented**: The Analytics component is correctly imported and added to the root layout file (web/app/layout.tsx)
3. **Implementation Follows Best Practices**: The setup matches the official Vercel documentation for Next.js App Router

## Files Reviewed
- `web/package.json` - Contains @vercel/analytics dependency (v2.0.1)
- `web/app/layout.tsx` - Contains Analytics component implementation:
  ```typescript
  import { Analytics } from "@vercel/analytics/next";
  // ... inside RootLayout component:
  <Analytics />
  ```

## Actions Taken
1. ✅ Fetched latest Vercel Analytics documentation to verify implementation
