## Implementation Details
The Analytics component is correctly placed in the root layout file, which is the recommended approach for Next.js App Router projects. It will automatically track page views across all routes in the application.

## Next Steps for Deployment
To fully enable Web Analytics:
1. Deploy the application to Vercel
2. Enable Web Analytics in the Vercel dashboard (Analytics section for your project)
3. After deployment, verify the analytics are working by checking browser Network tab for requests to the analytics endpoint
4. View analytics data in the Vercel dashboard after collecting sufficient traffic

